{"tid":1691492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】如果中資銀行總行電腦server故障會點","createTime":"2019-11-03T16:19:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T16:32:30.000Z","uid":220066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1fac4478fdb7a92674e83d7686920f45f70ffbdc","tid":1691492,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:19:32.000Z","msg":"自從中銀連Atm都改左星期一至星期六服務之後<br />\n屋企人覺得好撚唔方便，個個係咁㩒曬d錢走人<br />\n如果連中資銀行既電腦server都受到必殺技影響<br />\n有無可能影響到成個金融市場同埋銀行體系運作<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋全港巿民咪對中資銀行信心咪下降囉<br />\n<br />\n而家全線中銀分店都差唔多被人封曬圍板<br />\n如果總行個電腦server都受到必殺技影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣咪較到全港巿民恐慌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n千萬<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好</span>用各種招式去打敗電腦server<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係銀行唔比我㩒錢走人架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9577d4e52adf8b5d01541d73ccbd611c713d53a2","tid":1691492,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:20:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ef6457c6ba24638cb472553f9bbb65c482235a43","tid":1691492,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:21:12.000Z","msg":"點解TVB仲咁撚串？因為狙擊Group 得個6千人follow，我今晚要見到過萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1691361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1691361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"497e125aec464db26a27c977aed1ea60e1d52cd6","tid":1691492,"uid":312859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"港交所被搞會唔會仲嚴重?"},{"pid":"14788618ce7cf11e845b55d02dd117bcaaabbcd6","tid":1691492,"uid":56475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T16:24:51.000Z","msg":"可以點，攻擊Server, 保安咁嚴密"},{"pid":"0a97acdc988c6d9b99a1abd0d8420b8030e5e121","tid":1691492,"uid":220066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"497e125aec464d